Greetings Bible Enthusiast! 

Have you ever heard of the expression "Adam's ale"?
Well, presumably, the first man had only water to
drink.  So, "Adam's ale" is a quaint way of referring
to water.

The next time someone asks you if you've got something
to drink, you can reply, "Sure, how about a little 
"Adam's ale?"

I just thought you might like to know that - just in
case you didn't already!

Have a wonderful day! 
Jan 
