--FEATURED FUNNY: JOHNNY AND THE WHALE:

  Little Johnny was at Sea World, and was having a 
  wonderful time; but he absolutely refused to go to
  the show to see Shamu, the killer whale.  He would
  not say why he didn't want to go, and nothing
  grandma, grandma, mom, or dad said would change 
  his mind about it.

  Later, after he got home and was snuggling into
  his bed to go to sleep, he finally told his
  Mom his reason:.

  "Mommy," he said, "I didn't want to go see Shamu
  because yesterday Aunt Susie told me how exciting
  the show would be because they 'pick children from
  the audience to feed Shamu.'"

